{"tid":2127023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【立法會選舉●法律界】趁郭榮鏗或被DQ 梁美芬學生傳獲西環祝福「越級」挑戰","createTime":"2020-07-27T06:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T06:33:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f58b7d9586195e4eaf9600fdd1c78efe529ed9db","tid":2127023,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/75F7VRGRZ2N77XXTKHQ3QLAYLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2F75F7VRGRZ2N77XXTKHQ3QLAYLA%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=673b3a99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2F75F7VRGRZ2N77XXTKHQ3QLAYLA%2F&h=d47674e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/75F7VRGRZ2N77XXTKHQ3QLAYLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n法律界可算新一屆立法會選舉的焦點功能組別戰場，因為主持內會主席選舉而被港澳辦及中聯辦發炮的公民黨郭榮鏗，爭取連任要先避過DQ一關，逃不過被選舉主任查訊命運的郭榮鏗早已物色資深大狀為Plan B，有可能在稍後報名；建制派方面，除了前刑事檢控專員、資深大律師江樂士（Grenville Cross）或上陣，建制派消息更流傳中聯辦力棒立法會議員梁美芬學生、由馬恩國任主席的香港法學交流基金會的秘書長陳曉鋒「越級」挑戰。"},{"pid":"9d3f89c6a1f18771be308688e9386fc8bfd0ec62","tid":2127023,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"獻世派拎埋法律界呢席 以後政府就可以話連法律界都支持所有法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}